{"tid":974914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"他曬舊照　環抱巨乳辣師「雙手狂摸」！本尊現身…網暴動啦","createTime":"2019-01-09T08:52:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T10:20:00.000Z","uid":212399,"like":7,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a19528a8376c865b0806abee588cdc6ad99e9409","tid":974914,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:52:06.000Z","msg":"生活中心／綜合報導<br />\n誰准你亂摸！近日就有一名男網友在臉書曬出小時候和國小老師的舊照，但可別以為老師「恰北北」，這位女老師不但長相甜美，穿上胸前中空的爆乳上衣，兩團渾圓簡直就要蹦出來，相當「胸狠」，而照片中的男童則是任由自己的小手在老師的胸前遊走，讓許多網友看了也羨慕到暴動了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/09/1727060-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F09%2F1727060-XXL.jpg&h=0b8491c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲男童的雙手在女老師胸前不斷移動。（圖／翻攝自Thanchanok Jirekpreedamit臉書）<br />\n一名男網友在臉書社團「爆廢公社公開版」上傳了一張舊照片，「過年快到了整理家裡，找到小時候跟老師的合照」。只見照片中的男童，站在外型甜美的女老師旁，雙手還不安份地在老師胸前不斷移動，不過更吸睛的是，這位女老師穿著胸前中空的灰色緊身上衣，襯托出豪乳的渾圓雪白，乳溝之深，似乎連男童手中的玩具車都能塞得進去。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/09/1727061-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F09%2F1727061-XXL.jpg&h=9021dda7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女老師胸前深溝，似乎連男童的玩具車也能放進去。（圖／翻攝自Thanchanok Jirekpreedamit臉書）<br />\n照片PO出後，也引起網友們熱議，「為什麼我的老師都又老又醜」、「那麼小就懂得挑部位」、「好羨慕這個小胸手」、「年紀輕輕就當老司機」；不過也有網友質疑，當時的年代根本不會有美瞳放大片及爆乳中空裝。原來照片中這位女老師其實是泰國女模Thanchanok Jirekpreedamit所假扮的，長相甜美的她，有著不科學的姣好身材，個人臉書還有許多火辣養眼的照片，吸引超過20萬網友追蹤。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/09/1726952-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F09%2F1726952-XXL.jpg&h=4dd84731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼其實這名女老師是泰國女模Thanchanok Jirekpreedamit所假扮的。（圖／翻攝自Thanchanok Jirekpreedamit臉書）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/09/1726953-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F09%2F1726953-XXL.jpg&h=d67d0b5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=482523\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D482523&d=hQHqI7QPdakeD8NgugC8V%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=75141c0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D482523&h=bc5c37d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=482523</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://1.bp.blogspot.com/-29gzNgSBAVY/W0LTaDP0SsI/AAAAAAAAAuc/COH0zMr-iDwY3NhVk1_EkKlcGtAUUdTRACLcBGAs/s1600/FB_IMG_1531106091126.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-29gzNgSBAVY%2FW0LTaDP0SsI%2FAAAAAAAAAuc%2FCOH0zMr-iDwY3NhVk1_EkKlcGtAUUdTRACLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2FFB_IMG_1531106091126.jpg&h=12723413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/07/2d/f7/072df7bea8b6b7f782002c1946cdc8ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F07%2F2d%2Ff7%2F072df7bea8b6b7f782002c1946cdc8ae.png&h=0bc11e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/4a/ef/63/4aef632a9d545ec019e607e090a4eb85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2F4a%2Fef%2F63%2F4aef632a9d545ec019e607e090a4eb85.jpg&h=6d211411&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/e2/19/14/e21914893865e78dc0c38733f70b1c8f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Fe2%2F19%2F14%2Fe21914893865e78dc0c38733f70b1c8f.jpg&h=598f9f19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a78f3fa675498b3a545aaea830a58368faafe863","tid":974914,"uid":199251,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:54:07.000Z","msg":"假架啲奶！"},{"pid":"55b2fdc36e3bb886c6d430db32a2aa4bf685d62c","tid":974914,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T08:54:50.000Z","msg":"P到呢"},{"pid":